{"thig4.1:0.1":"Therigatha 4.1 ","thig4.1:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thig4.1:0.3":"Bhaddakapilanitherigatha ","thig4.1:1.1":"“Putto buddhassa dayado, ","thig4.1:1.2":"kassapo susamahito; ","thig4.1:1.3":"Pubbenivasam yovedi, ","thig4.1:1.4":"saggapayanca passati. ","thig4.1:2.1":"Atho jatikkhayam patto, ","thig4.1:2.2":"abhinnavosito muni; ","thig4.1:2.3":"Etahi tihi vijjahi, ","thig4.1:2.4":"tevijjo hoti brahmano. ","thig4.1:3.1":"Tatheva bhadda kapilani, ","thig4.1:3.2":"tevijja maccuhayini; ","thig4.1:3.3":"Dhareti antimam deham, ","thig4.1:3.4":"jetva maram savahinim. ","thig4.1:4.1":"Disva adinavam loke, ","thig4.1:4.2":"ubho pabbajita mayam; ","thig4.1:4.3":"Tyamha khinasava danta, ","thig4.1:4.4":"sitibhutamha nibbuta”ti. ","thig4.1:5.1":"… Bhadda kapilani theri …. ","thig4.1:6.1":"Catukkanipato nitthito. "}